subtitleNullable: How do we search for food? Google search interest can reveal key food trends over the years.
descriptionNullable:
This is the data behind the Rhythm of Food visualisation by Moritz Stefaner. It shows seasonal food searches in different food types around the world since 2004. The data is indexed, with 0 being the least and 100 being the highest search interest.

Find out more here: http://rhythm-of-food.net/
